# PixelBreaker

PixelBreaker is a 2D Breakout-style arcade game built in C++ with OpenGL.  
It features custom rendering, input handling, power-ups, and polished effects.

---

## Setup Instructions (Windows + Visual Studio)

### 1. Install vcpkg (once)
If you don’t already have vcpkg:
```powershell
git clone https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg
cd vcpkg
.\bootstrap-vcpkg.bat
.\vcpkg integrate install
